---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { QUOTE, SITE_TITLE } from "@/consts";
---

<div
  class="fixed inset-0 -z-10 bg-cover bg-center"
  style="background-image:url('/surpgio_background.png');"
></div>


<section
  id="hero"
  class="relative w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 py-8 sm:py-10 min-h-[80dvh] md:min-h-[70dvh] overflow-visible"
>
  <div
    class="w-full max-w-3xl rounded-2xl text-white flex flex-col justify-center shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm"
    style="
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(108, 92, 231, 0.78), rgba(72, 61, 156, 0.78));
      padding: clamp(16px, 4vw, 48px);
    "
  >
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-prose">
      <h1 class="text-[clamp(20px,5vw,28px)] font-semibold leading-tight text-[#dfe6e9] text-center [text-wrap:balance]">
        About <span class="font-bold">Sexy Unique RPG</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-[#dfe6e9] leading-relaxed text-[clamp(14px,3.5vw,18px)]">
        <p>
          <b>Sexy Unique RPG</b> is a 16-bit style, top-down RPG inspired by the early seasons of Vanderpump Rules.
          Set in a pixelated West Hollywood, you play as a new server at SUR (Sexy Unique Restaurant), where the tips
          are low and the stakes are high.
        </p>

        <p>
          Talk to AI-powered versions of the cast, stir up drama, and try to survive the social minefield of WeHo
          nightlife, all under the watchful eye of Lisa Vanderpump.
        </p>

        <p>
          The game is a fictionalized take on the Vanderpump Rules universe, with original storylines and scenes that
          expand over time. Two chaotic episodes are available now, with more on the way.
        </p>

        <p>
          Currently open from 5–10 PM PT. Server drama is expensive when you’re literally paying for server time.
          Best played on a desktop browser; mobile support is limited.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        id="about-bottom"
        class="mt-5 text-center font-bold text-[clamp(16px,4vw,20px)]"
        style="color:#55efc4;"
      >
        Serve drinks. Start drama. Become a legend.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
